title: Valve Just Surprise Dropped the Steam Machine

author: Austin Evans
description:
The PS5 is 5 years old and has been wildly successful by the numbers...but did Sony actually deliver on what they promised back in 2020? With Xbox pivoting away from the console war, I'm worried Sony's gotten way too comfortable.
